section.def:
Commissioner
                                                (署長) means the
                                    Commissioner of Correctional Services;

committee
                                                (委員會) means the
                                    committee established by section 6;

fund
                                                (基金) means the
                                    fund established by section 3;

trustee
                                                (受託人) means the
                                    Commissioner as trustee of the fund;
